dw1.jpg?v=1761805027"},{"product_id":"the-shawshank-redemption-movie-3-piece-set","title":"The Shawshank Redemption | Movie | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp\u003eBring home one of cinema’s most iconic moments with this 3-piece split poster inspired by *The Shawshank Redemption*. The warm glowing tones, powerful silhouette and the quote “Hope can set you free, but fear can hold you prisoner” create a bold and emotional centrepiece for any room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePrinted on premium 300 GSM matte photo paper, each panel delivers rich colours, sharp details and a smooth anti-glare finish. The 3-piece split layout adds depth and presence, making it perfect for bedrooms, studios, offices or cinematic room setups.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA must-have for movie lovers, motivational art fans and anyone who connects with the timeless message of hope, freedom and resilience.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394462712104,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394462744872,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394462777640,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/w_c65b7809-0e81-47c6-b63c-92af62939004.webp?v=1763209508"},{"product_id":"the-upside-down-awakens-stranger-things-01-3-piece-set","title":"The Upside Down Awakens | Stranger Things #01 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"1027\"\u003eStep into the dark world of the Upside Down with this electrifying \u003cstrong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"744\"\u003eStranger Things concept poster\u003c\/strong\u003e, featuring powerful fantasy-style artwork inspired by the show’s iconic Season 4 villain — \u003cstrong data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"845\"\u003eVecna\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003cbr data-start=\"846\" data-end=\"849\"\u003eSurrounded by glowing red lightning and floating D20 dice, the poster fuses the essence of \u003cstrong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"962\"\u003eDungeons \u0026amp; Dragons\u003c\/strong\u003e with the sinister atmosphere of Hawkins’ most terrifying threat.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1367\"\u003eAt the forefront stands a heroic party — an archer, a warrior, a bard, and a fire-wielding mage — symbolizing the fearless energy of the show’s beloved characters as they face off against supernatural evil.\u003cbr data-start=\"1235\" data-end=\"1238\"\u003eThe intense red palette, dynamic poses, and cinematic lighting make this piece a perfect centerpiece for any Stranger Things fan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1369\" data-end=\"1491\"\u003eIdeal for bedrooms, gaming rooms, studios, and collectors, this poster turns your space into a gateway to the Upside Down.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461925672,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461958440,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461991208,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/W_0d4843cc-f724-4617-a668-e4d6dfeefe7c.webp?v=1764594072"},{"product_id":"king-steve-harrington-stranger-things-01-3-piece-set","title":"King Steve Harrington | Stranger Things #00 | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"241\" data-end=\"575\"\u003eCelebrate the unbeatable charm and fearless attitude of \u003cstrong data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"311\"\u003eKing Steve\u003c\/strong\u003e with this stunning, high-detail concept poster inspired by his iconic heroic moments.\u003cbr data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"400\"\u003eThis artwork captures Steve in full battle-ready mode leather jacket, nail-studded bat, and that signature confident stare that made him a fan-favorite protector of Hawkins.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"803\"\u003eSet against a dramatic red-and-blue Upside Down–inspired background, the poster blends \u003cstrong data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"688\"\u003egraphic-novel energy\u003c\/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong data-start=\"690\" data-end=\"712\"\u003ecinematic lighting\u003c\/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong data-start=\"718\" data-end=\"737\"\u003ebold typography\u003c\/strong\u003e to create a powerful statement piece for any Stranger Things fan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"1024\"\u003eEvery detail, from the stylized shadows to the glowing red atmosphere, reflects the intensity of the world Steve fights to protect reminding everyone why he is more than just “\u003cstrong\u003eKing Steve\u003c\/strong\u003e”… he is the heart of the team.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-end=\"1491\" data-start=\"1369\"\u003eIdeal for bedrooms, gaming rooms, studios, and collectors, this poster turns your space into a gateway to the Upside Down.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394460254504,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394460287272,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394460320040,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/stevew1.jpg?v=1766055004"},{"product_id":"the-golden-trio-harrypotter-friendship-art-poster-3-piece-set","title":"The Golden Trio | Harrypotter Friendship Art | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"509\"\u003eCelebrate the heart of the wizarding world with \u003cstrong data-start=\"383\" data-end=\"404\"\u003e“The Golden Trio”\u003c\/strong\u003e, a soft, emotional fan-art illustration inspired by the timeless friendship of Harry, Hermione, and Ron.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"855\"\u003eRendered in a delicate watercolor style with warm golden light, this artwork captures a quiet, meaningful moment — smiles filled with hope, loyalty, and memories that last forever. The gentle expressions, flowing textures, and subtle magical atmosphere make this piece feel nostalgic, comforting, and deeply personal for every Harry Potter fan.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"857\" data-end=\"1090\"\u003ePerfect for bedrooms, study spaces, reading corners, or gift collections, this poster is a reminder that \u003cem data-start=\"962\" data-end=\"1005\"\u003ethe ones who love us never truly leave us\u003c\/em\u003e. A must-have for Potterheads who value friendship, courage, and magic beyond spells.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1092\" data-end=\"1201\"\u003ePrinted on premium matte paper for a soft, artistic finish that enhances the illustration’s depth and warmth.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis is an unofficial fan-made artwork. Not affiliated with or endorsed by Warner Bros. or J.K. Rowling.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394459926824,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394459959592,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394459992360,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/TheGoldenTrioHarrypotterFriendshipArtPoster3PieceSet_1.webp?v=1766646205"},{"product_id":"conquer-the-void-interstellar-motivational-movie-3-piece-set","title":"Conquer the Void | Interstellar | Motivational Movie | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"322\" data-end=\"639\"\u003eStep into the infinite with \u003cstrong\u003eConquer the Void | Interstellar | Motivational Movie | 3 Piece Set\u003c\/strong\u003e, a striking monochrome cosmic artwork inspired by the awe and mystery of deep space. Set against a vast star field, a lone cosmic traveler stands before a colossal gravitational phenomenon, symbolizing courage, curiosity, and humanity’s endless pursuit of the unknown.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"641\" data-end=\"961\"\u003eThe dramatic contrast of light and shadow, combined with intricate space textures and cinematic scale, makes this artwork powerful yet minimal. It evokes themes of exploration, insignificance, and transcendence — perfect for science fiction enthusiasts, space lovers, and those drawn to bold, thought-provoking wall art.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"963\" data-end=\"1272\"\u003eDesigned to command attention in modern interiors, studios, gaming rooms, and creative spaces, this piece brings a sense of scale and wonder to any wall. Printed with a premium matte finish to preserve fine details and depth, it delivers an immersive visual experience that feels both futuristic and timeless.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394459107624,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394459140392,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394459173160,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/1_e3e7e8fc-3288-48e2-af7e-b14a5026c8d5.webp?v=1767869636"},{"product_id":"i-m-not-a-traitor-peaky-blinders-series-3-piece-set","title":"I m Not A Traitor | Peaky Blinders Series | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"287\" data-end=\"606\"\u003eStep into a world ruled by loyalty, power, and unshakable resolve with \u003cstrong data-start=\"358\" data-end=\"417\"\u003eI’m Not a Traitor | Peaky Blinders Series | 3 Piece Set\u003c\/strong\u003e. Set against a rain-soaked industrial street drenched in deep crimson tones, this artwork captures a lone figure walking forward with calm authority — fearless, composed, and unapologetic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"930\"\u003eThe bold red typography slicing through the shadows reinforces the message of defiance and class, while the dramatic lighting, smoke-filled background, and period detailing create a raw cinematic atmosphere. Every element reflects themes of honor, control, ambition, and standing one’s ground in a world built on betrayal.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"932\" data-end=\"1233\"\u003eDesigned to command attention, this 3-piece set is perfect for modern interiors, offices, studios, gaming rooms, and statement walls. Printed with a premium matte finish to enhance depth, contrast, and texture, this artwork delivers a powerful visual presence that feels intense, iconic, and timeless.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394458943784,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394458976552,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394459009320,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/thw1.jpg?v=1767953487"},{"product_id":"billy-butcher-daddy-s-home-the-boys-3-piece-set","title":"Billy Butcher | Daddys Home | The Boys | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"295\" data-end=\"624\"\u003eBring the ruthless charisma of \u003cstrong data-start=\"326\" data-end=\"343\"\u003eBilly Butcher\u003c\/strong\u003e straight to your wall with this bold, cinematic split poster inspired by \u003cem data-start=\"417\" data-end=\"427\"\u003eThe Boys\u003c\/em\u003e. Designed in a high-impact comic-realism art style, this artwork captures Butcher’s intense glare, his signature crowbar, and the raw red palette that symbolizes his unforgiving war against supes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"983\"\u003ePerfect for fans who love gritty anti-heroes, dark humor, and high-energy room décor, this premium wall art instantly transforms your setup into a tribute to one of TV’s most iconic characters. Printed on thick matte art paper for rich detail and studio-quality color, it becomes a powerful centrepiece for gaming setups, bedrooms, and collectors' displays.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"985\" data-end=\"1148\"\u003eWhether you’re building a supe-free zone or just love Butcher’s uncompromising personality, this artwork is made to dominate your wall — just like the man himself.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394458779944,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394458812712,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394458845480,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/BillyButcherDaddy_sHomeTheBoys3PieceSet_1.jpg?v=1768910926"},{"product_id":"no-excuses-the-lone-penguin-motivational-3-piece-set","title":"No Excuses | The Lone PENGUIN | Motivational | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"52\" data-end=\"543\"\u003eBring a sharp, no-nonsense mindset to your space with the \u003cstrong data-start=\"110\" data-end=\"146\"\u003e“NO EXCUSES” Motivational Poster\u003c\/strong\u003e—a cinematic Antarctic landscape built for people who want progress, not comfort. The scene is intentionally minimal and powerful: an endless snowfield, distant glacier-cut mountains, and a lone penguin walking forward with a quiet trail behind it. It’s a visual metaphor for discipline—showing that real momentum is created when the environment is harsh, the path is long, and nobody is watching.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"545\" data-end=\"941\"\u003eThe bold, oversized \u003cstrong data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"579\"\u003eNO EXCUSES\u003c\/strong\u003e typography is designed to hit instantly from across the room, making it perfect for daily reinforcement in high-focus spaces like a \u003cstrong data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"772\"\u003ehome office, study setup, gym, workstation, or dorm room\u003c\/strong\u003e. The supporting quote adds depth without clutter, keeping the overall look clean, premium, and modern—more like a cinematic film poster than a basic motivational print.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1261\"\u003eWhether you’re building habits, chasing a goal, preparing for exams, working on your body, or simply upgrading your room aesthetics, this artwork is made to keep you moving when motivation fades. It also makes a strong gift for students, creators, entrepreneurs, athletes, and anyone who respects consistency and grit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1416\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1276\"\u003eBest for:\u003c\/strong\u003e Office wall decor, gym motivation, study room focus, minimalist aesthetic rooms, productivity corners, and gift-worthy goal-setting spaces.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394458616104,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394458648872,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394458681640,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/NoExcusesTheLonePENGUINMotivational_2.webp?v=1769240044"},{"product_id":"the-bride-samurai-aesthetic-kill-bill-3-piece-set","title":"The Bride Samurai Aesthetic | Kill Bill | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"456\" data-end=\"617\"\u003eBring the legendary revenge saga to your walls with this \u003cstrong data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"550\"\u003eKill Bill Vol.1 Split Wall Poster\u003c\/strong\u003e featuring \u003cem data-start=\"561\" data-end=\"572\"\u003eThe Bride\u003c\/em\u003e in her iconic yellow suit, ready for battle.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"829\"\u003eDesigned with a bold cinematic composition, this artwork captures the intensity of the classic scene — the katana drawn, the coiled snake behind her, and the powerful typography that defines the legendary film.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"1016\"\u003eThis \u003cstrong data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"864\"\u003e3-panel split poster set\u003c\/strong\u003e creates a striking wall aesthetic, perfect for movie lovers, anime-style art fans, and anyone who wants their space to reflect a strong cinematic vibe.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1018\" data-end=\"1181\"\u003ePrinted on \u003cstrong data-start=\"1029\" data-end=\"1067\"\u003epremium 300 GSM matte finish paper\u003c\/strong\u003e, this poster set delivers sharp details, deep colors, and a gallery-style look that instantly upgrades your wall.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1294\"\u003ePerfect for:\u003cbr\u003e• Gaming setups\u003cbr data-start=\"1211\" data-end=\"1214\"\u003e• Bedroom aesthetic walls\u003cbr data-start=\"1239\" data-end=\"1242\"\u003e• Movie room décor\u003cbr data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1263\"\u003e• Anime and action movie fans\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1296\" data-end=\"1373\"\u003eCreate a bold and powerful wall with this \u003cstrong data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1372\"\u003eKill Bill aesthetic poster set\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1596\"\u003e✨ \u003cstrong data-start=\"1377\" data-end=\"1397\"\u003eProduct Features\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e• Premium \u003cstrong data-start=\"1408\" data-end=\"1431\"\u003e300 GSM matte paper\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1431\" data-end=\"1434\"\u003e• \u003cstrong dat